high_descs: Walk ahead and slightly right to the front of the coffee table.
Pick up the trophy closest to you.
Turn around and walk to the table.
Place the trophy near the edge of the table.
Turn around and walk to the far side of the table, closest to the couch.
Pick up the trophy on the right side.
Walk back to the table.
Put the trophy on the table to the right of the first trophy.
anns.task_desc: Put two trophies on a table.

high_descs: Turn left then right to face the coffee table.
Pick up the statue closest to the edge.
Turn left then left walk to the dining table.
Place the statue on the dining table.
Turn around, walk past the coffee table, make a right, turn right to face the coffee table.
Pick up the statue closest to the edge.
Turn right then left around the coffee table, walk to the dining table.
Place the statue to the right of the original statue.
anns.task_desc: Move two statues from the coffee table to the dining table.

high_descs: Walk to the coffee table the is in front of you off to the left.
Pick up the black statue that is closest to you
Turn around and head to the table in front of you.
Place the statue on the table
Turn around and head to the other side of the coffee table in front of you.
Pick up the statue on the right
Head across the room to the table in front of you.
Place the statue on the table to the right of the previously placed statue.
